src:
RBK-profil: – Havner vi utenfor Europa, er det en stor skandale
01 Nov 2019, 20:36 by Anne-Marit Dahl,Ole K. Sagbakken
– Nå må vi redde stumpene, erkjenner Pål André Helland som i noen minutter trodde han ble matchvinner mot Strømsgodset.

Strømsgodset - Rosenborg 3–3 (1–1)
text:
RBK profile: - If we get outside Europe, it is a big scandal
01 Nov 2019, 20:36 by Anne-Marit Dahl, Ole K. Sagbakken
- Now we have to save the stumps, admits Pål André Helland who for a few minutes thought he was the match winner against Strømsgodset.

Strømsgodset - Rosenborg 3–3 (1–1)
